                                "stop": 9.272,
                                "byte_start": 86850,
                                "byte_stop": 123944,
                                "text": "The opinion of the Court in number 94-558 and a related case United States versus Hays will be announced by Justice O\u2019Connor."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 9.272,
                        "stop": 169.9,
